description:
Interested in learning directly from Chick? Join the Chick Corea Academy today! Click here now: https://www.chickcoreaacademy.com/
 
Chick on the magic behind his trio with Christian McBride & Brian Blade: "There's all kinds of ways to surprise each other. I never know what they're going to do." Trilogy 2 is out now! Grab a copy here: https://found.ee/CCTrio_Trilogy2
